Package: cnv.methyl
Title: cnv.methyl finds copy number alteration from methylation idat files
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(c("Izar", "Llaquet"), "de Villasante", , "idevillasante@carrerasresearch.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-7325-0631 "))
Description: The package implements an automatic and dynamic thresholding
    algorithm to find somatic copy number alterations in methylation
    arrays based on log2R intensities. It relies mostly on minfi for
    preprocessing and and conumee for segmentation.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
